Package planeair.components.mapview.mapwp

Class MapWaypoint

java.lang.Object
org.jxmapviewer.beans.AbstractBean
org.jxmapviewer.viewer.DefaultWaypoint
planeair.components.mapview.mapwp.MapWaypoint
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.jxmapviewer.viewer.Waypoint
Direct Known Subclasses:
AirportWaypoint, FlightWaypoint
public abstract class MapWaypoint extends org.jxmapviewer.viewer.DefaultWaypoint
This class puts interactive Waypoints on the Application's map. The MapWaypoints are Waypoints with a JButton and an icon, which makes them clickable . This class is abstract, and can only be instanced throught one of its children (AirportWaypoint, FlightWaypoint...)
Author:
Luc le Manifik
